column2: SELECT TOP # my.OBJECT, my.RA, my.DEC, e.bptclass, s.z, z.t0#_spiral_a0#_spiral_flag, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err, g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_reqw, g.h_alpha_reqw_err, g.oiii_#_reqw, g.oiii_#_reqw_err from MyDB.PTF_objects AS my CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (my.RA, my.DEC, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON p.objid = o.objid JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN zoo2MainSpecz as z on z.specobjid = p.specobjid JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE z.t0#_spiral_a0#_spiral_flag = #
